            <title>Redmi Watch 4 明日發表，金屬錶殼 + 快拆錶帶 + 近兩吋螢幕</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2023/11/28/redmi-watch-4-announce-tomorrow/life-tech/watch-wireless-home/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=redmi-watch-4-announce-tomorrow</link>
