        <item>
            <title>勞斯萊斯首款純電動車 Spectre 亮相澳門，預計將於 2030 年底全面實現電動化</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2023/11/27/rolls-royces-first-pure-electric-car-specter-unveiled-at-wynn-palace-in-macau/life-tech/auto/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=rolls-royces-first-pure-electric-car-specter-unveiled-at-wynn-palace-in-macau</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2023/11/27/rolls-royces-first-pure-electric-car-specter-unveiled-at-wynn-palace-in-macau/life-tech/auto/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[蔣納偲]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Mon, 27 Nov 2023 12:05:25 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[車壇動向]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Spectre]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[勞斯萊斯]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1207033</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>勞斯萊斯汽車（香港及澳門）早前於澳門永利皇宮舉行晚宴，慶祝勞斯萊斯首款電動車 Spectre 亮相。勞斯萊斯為是次晚宴於澳門永利皇宮的戶外草坪上搭建大型帳篷，吸引超過 200 位貴賓和媒體出席。</p><p><img decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1207040" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Image-1-694x417.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="417" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Image-1-694x417.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Image-1-1280x770.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Image-1-768x462.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Image-1-1536x924.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Image-1-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>勞斯萊斯即日起至 2023 年 12 月 1 日，將會在澳門永利皇宮北翼大堂舉行「Spirit Electrified: Rolls-Royce Spectre」期間限定展覽，訪客可近距離觀看勞斯萊斯全球首款電動超級轎跑車（Ultra-Luxury Electric Super Coupé）。</p><p><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1207041" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Image-6-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Image-6-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Image-6-1280x853.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Image-6-768x512.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Image-6-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Image-6-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>勞斯萊斯汽車（香港及澳門）總經理 Janice Lai 表示：「Spectre 首先是一部純粹的勞斯萊斯，其次才是一部電動車。」並且表示勞斯萊斯將於 2030 年底全面實現電動化。</p><p>據瞭解，Spectre 曾在 2021 年 9 月開始進行路試，在各種極端地形和天氣下形式超過 250 萬公里。</p><h2>外型設計優化風阻係數</h2><p>Spectre 使用了分體式前大燈，採用拋光不鏽鋼打造格柵。萬神殿進氣格柵葉片可有助引導汽車前方的氣流。</p><p><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-1207052" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Spectre-Unveiling-Spectre-Exterior-Image-Front-Grille-1.jpg" alt="" width="10824" height="7522" /></p><p>「歡慶女神」雕像也經過空氣動力學重新設計調校。</p><p><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1207053" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Spectre-Unveiling-Spectre-Exterior-Image-Front-Spirit-of-Ecstasy-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Spectre-Unveiling-Spectre-Exterior-Image-Front-Spirit-of-Ecstasy-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Spectre-Unveiling-Spectre-Exterior-Image-Front-Spirit-of-Ecstasy-1280x853.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Spectre-Unveiling-Spectre-Exterior-Image-Front-Spirit-of-Ecstasy-768x512.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Spectre-Unveiling-Spectre-Exterior-Image-Front-Spirit-of-Ecstasy.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>車身俐落的弧形線條令 Spectre 成為勞斯萊斯空氣動力學表現最佳的車型，風阻係數僅 0.25cd。</p><p><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1207054" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Spectre-Unveiling-Spectre-Exterior-Hero-Image-Side-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Spectre-Unveiling-Spectre-Exterior-Hero-Image-Side-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Spectre-Unveiling-Spectre-Exterior-Hero-Image-Side-1280x720.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Spectre-Unveiling-Spectre-Exterior-Hero-Image-Side-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Spectre-Unveiling-Spectre-Exterior-Hero-Image-Side-1536x864.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Spectre-Unveiling-Spectre-Exterior-Hero-Image-Side-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>車側底部的「飄馳線」靈感源於遊艇設計，車尾燈至於勞斯萊斯有史以來最大的一體式側後車身面板，該側後車身面板從 A 柱延伸至車尾箱。Spectre 採用垂直排列的車尾燈，內置燈殼本身無著色，客戶在定製時可選擇不同的顏色搭配。 <img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1207056" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Spectre-Unveiling-Spectre-Exterior-Image-Rear-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Spectre-Unveiling-Spectre-Exterior-Image-Rear-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Spectre-Unveiling-Spectre-Exterior-Image-Rear-1280x853.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Spectre-Unveiling-Spectre-Exterior-Image-Rear-768x512.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Spectre-Unveiling-Spectre-Exterior-Image-Rear.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1207055" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Spectre-Unveiling-Spectre-Exterior-Image-Rear-Light-1-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Spectre-Unveiling-Spectre-Exterior-Image-Rear-Light-1-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Spectre-Unveiling-Spectre-Exterior-Image-Rear-Light-1-1280x854.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Spectre-Unveiling-Spectre-Exterior-Image-Rear-Light-1-768x512.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Spectre-Unveiling-Spectre-Exterior-Image-Rear-Light-1-1536x1025.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Spectre-Unveiling-Spectre-Exterior-Image-Rear-Light-1.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>車輪方面則使用了 23 吋輪圈。</p><h2><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1207051" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Spectre-Unveiling-Spectre-Exterior-Image-Side-Wheel-1-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Spectre-Unveiling-Spectre-Exterior-Image-Side-Wheel-1-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Spectre-Unveiling-Spectre-Exterior-Image-Side-Wheel-1-1280x853.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Spectre-Unveiling-Spectre-Exterior-Image-Side-Wheel-1-768x512.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Spectre-Unveiling-Spectre-Exterior-Image-Side-Wheel-1.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></h2><h2>個性化內飾設計</h2><p>Spectre 是勞斯萊斯首款配備星光車門（Starlight Doors）的量產車型，以 4,796 顆柔和光電於車門勾畫出星空。而星光飾板（Illuminated Fascia）延續夜空主題。星光飾板上有超過 5,500 顆「星星」圍繞 Spectre 字標。星光飾板位於乘客位前方的中控台，在汽車未啟動時不會點亮。</p><p><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1207044" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Spectre-Unveiling-Spectre-Interior-Image-StarHeadliner-1-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Spectre-Unveiling-Spectre-Interior-Image-StarHeadliner-1-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Spectre-Unveiling-Spectre-Interior-Image-StarHeadliner-1-1280x853.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Spectre-Unveiling-Spectre-Interior-Image-StarHeadliner-1-768x512.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Spectre-Unveiling-Spectre-Interior-Image-StarHeadliner-1.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1207046" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Spectre-Unveiling-Spectre-Interior-Image-Door-Cabin-Dark-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Spectre-Unveiling-Spectre-Interior-Image-Door-Cabin-Dark-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Spectre-Unveiling-Spectre-Interior-Image-Door-Cabin-Dark-1280x853.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Spectre-Unveiling-Spectre-Interior-Image-Door-Cabin-Dark-768x512.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Spectre-Unveiling-Spectre-Interior-Image-Door-Cabin-Dark.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>Spectre 亦搭載全新設計的 SPIRIT 軟件系統，可操控汽車各項功能，與 Whispers 應用程式配合，讓客戶與汽車進行遠程溝通，接受由勞斯萊斯專家提供的資訊。在 SPIRIT 軟件系統支援下，Spectre 可提供個性化的數碼儀錶板設計，客戶可定製儀錶板的專屬顏色。</p><p><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1207047" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Spectre-Unveiling-Spectre-Interior-Image-Dials-Night-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Spectre-Unveiling-Spectre-Interior-Image-Dials-Night-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Spectre-Unveiling-Spectre-Interior-Image-Dials-Night-1280x853.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Spectre-Unveiling-Spectre-Interior-Image-Dials-Night-768x512.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Spectre-Unveiling-Spectre-Interior-Image-Dials-Night.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1207048" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Spectre-Unveiling-Spectre-Interior-Image-Dashboard-exterior-view-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Spectre-Unveiling-Spectre-Interior-Image-Dashboard-exterior-view-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Spectre-Unveiling-Spectre-Interior-Image-Dashboard-exterior-view-1280x853.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Spectre-Unveiling-Spectre-Interior-Image-Dashboard-exterior-view-768x512.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Spectre-Unveiling-Spectre-Interior-Image-Dashboard-exterior-view.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>特別一提的是，Spectre 的內飾設計已預留空間供客戶訂製縫線、刺繡和滾邊等。</p><p><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1207050" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Image-19-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Image-19-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Image-19-1280x853.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Image-19-768x512.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Image-19-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Image-19-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>數碼工程方面，Spectre 透過「去中心化智能」軟件技術，在距離數據源更近的位置處理數據，而非全交由單一中央處理器處理。因此，Spectre 搭載了 14.12 萬組收發裝置特製專屬的手動控件，並且針對不同氣候、行駛速度、道路類型、汽車狀態和駕駛風格設計額外的可變量子功能。</p><p>Spectre 採用全鋁質車架，以四個定點支撐對應車身四角，增加其靈活性和擴展性。並且將電池結構整合在全鋁質車架之中，讓 Spectre 比以往的勞斯萊斯汽車剛度，提高了 30%。並且車輛底板通道設置在結構框架中，而非框架上面或下方，為電池和地板之間的佈線管道留出空間。架構設計也讓電池擁有相當於 700 公斤的隔音材質。</p><p><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1207057" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Spectre-Unveiling-Spectre-Exterior-Hero-Image-Front-3-4-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Spectre-Unveiling-Spectre-Exterior-Hero-Image-Front-3-4-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Spectre-Unveiling-Spectre-Exterior-Hero-Image-Front-3-4-1280x720.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Spectre-Unveiling-Spectre-Exterior-Hero-Image-Front-3-4-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Spectre-Unveiling-Spectre-Exterior-Hero-Image-Front-3-4-1536x864.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Spectre-Unveiling-Spectre-Exterior-Hero-Image-Front-3-4-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><h2> 最新影片</h2><div class="video-container"><iframe loading="lazy" title="最新影片" width="500" height="281" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/videoseries?list=PLiEPZioiGtHw9_9gm4Ty0_pTEviOKNvfl" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen=""></iframe></div>

